Thank you for making our holiday @galmeetsglam launch today so amazing!!! The support means everything to us- our team works tirelessly for YOU! Ever since starting @galmeetsglam I have a whole new level of appreciation and admiration for a single garment. The amount of work that goes behind that item, the amount of hands that touch that sole piece, the thought and attention to every detail from fabric to drape to design and fit, and then reworking and redoing until it’s perfect. I am not alone in this, I have an incredible team (we are small but mighty) and we all share the same passion and mission: to create beautiful dresses for women to feel amazing in. I’ve never felt so passionate and wanted something so much my entire life. I am beyond grateful to have an amazing community who supports me (YOU!!!) and a team who lets me lead them. My heart is full today ❤️ #gmgcollection #gmgonme
